                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 803.51/1342.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Minister</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-02-20T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 20, 1913—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Owing to uncertain political and financial conditions here in the near future,
                    the American group is seriously contemplating withdrawal from the present loan
                    negotiations unless the contract is signed without further delay. Report fully
                    upon the possible cause of delay and the prospects of early signature.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Knox</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
